{"id":"jaaziah","term":"Jaaziah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Comforted by Jehovah, a descendant of Merari the Levite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 24:26\">1 Chr. 24:26</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 24:27\">27</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 24:26","1 Chronicles 24:27"]}